description: Local BBQ that's on the move! jimmy ray's is serving up the highest quality in BBQ, grilling, and fantastic service. Years of experience and traditional family recipes make sure that every bite will have that down home feel and gourmet taste you'll love. Whether it's the BBQ ribs, the pulled pork, the roast chicken, or any of their mouthwatering cuisine, jimmy ray's bar-b-que will leave you happy and satisfied!
name: jimmy ray's bar-b-que
